00:43:07.570 --> 00:43:09.235 align:middle line:84%
as science, religion,
and mythology.

00:43:09.235 --> 00:43:12.325 align:middle line:90%


00:43:12.325 --> 00:43:14.420 align:middle line:84%
With much of her
writing over the years,

00:43:14.420 --> 00:43:18.490 align:middle line:84%
questions have been raised
