00:43:25.210 --> 00:43:27.830 align:middle line:84%
But she did try
to give citations,

00:43:27.830 --> 00:43:30.840 align:middle line:84%
and was adhering to the
standards of the day

00:43:30.840 --> 00:43:34.340 align:middle line:90%
as best she was able to.

00:43:34.340 --> 00:43:37.730 align:middle line:84%
She never deliberately
misrepresents

00:43:37.730 --> 00:43:41.120 align:middle line:84%
the content of any spiritual
