00:43:46.280 --> 00:43:49.820 align:middle line:84%
as somebody participating
in the intellectual debates

00:43:49.820 --> 00:43:50.320 align:middle line:90%
of her time.

00:43:50.320 --> 00:43:54.110 align:middle line:90%


00:43:54.110 --> 00:43:57.860 align:middle line:84%
>>I think if her work
had not been completed,

00:43:57.860 --> 00:44:03.200 align:middle line:84%
and she would have continued
