00:44:09.790 --> 00:44:11.860 align:middle line:90%
They knew she was dying.

00:44:11.860 --> 00:44:13.080 align:middle line:90%
And off she went.

00:44:13.080 --> 00:44:15.090 align:middle line:90%
It was that simple.

00:44:15.090 --> 00:44:15.600 align:middle line:90%
Age 59.

00:44:15.600 --> 00:44:20.240 align:middle line:90%


00:44:20.240 --> 00:44:24.435 align:middle line:10%
>>Every big newspaper in the
